==English==
===Noun===
'''diaeresis''' ([[diaereses]]) (''British'')

====Alternative spellings====
*[[dieresis]] (''especially US'')

#A [[diacritic]] ( ¨ ) placed over a [[vowel]] to show that it is to be pronounced separately from an adjacent vowel (as in ''coördinate'', an older spelling of [[coordinate]], and ''Zoë''.

====Note====
*Although this symbol has the same form as the [[umlaut]], it has as a different function and so these two terms are not interchangeable.

